            <p>You can look forward to improved health, vitality and a renewed sense of wellness after your treatment.</p>
            <a class="btn btn--gold" href="/book-appointment/">Book Your Appointment</a>
          </div>
          <div class="disc"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/MEDITATION-ROOM-1-rkuf574i9372gylbszubqtan2hqqdz66wrlvg4zp0w.webp" alt="Ayurveda Experiences in Bondi Junction, Sydney" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy" /></div>
